Template: openstreetmap-mapnik-data/initdb
Type: boolean
Default: true
Description: Create and initialize the mysql-table?
 Do you want to run 
       geoinfo.pl --create-db --create-defaults
 to initialize your database and add defaults into it.

Template: openstreetmap-mapnik-data/grant_user
Type: string
Default: *
